overview.en: FBTT is a commercial token that provides value recognition, connection and transmission for service and consumer in foreign exchange market. By consuming FBTT, it can obtain products and services equivalent to FBTT.
overview.zh: FBTT是为外汇交易市场的服务与消费方，提供价值认可、连接、传递的商业化代币，通过消耗FBTT，获得与FBTT等价的产品、服务
